## 🔢 제어흐름 예시

### 예: 조건문 (if-else)

```
PUSH 10          # x = 10
PUSH 5           # y = 5
LT               # x < y? [0]
JIT(else_label)  # if true, jump to else
PUSH 100         # then: return 100
JMP(end_label)   # jump to end
(else_label:)
PUSH 200         # else: return 200
(end_label:)
PRINT            # print result
HALT 0
```

### 예: 루프

```
PUSH 5           # counter = 5
(loop:)
INCR             # counter++
DUP              # duplicate counter
PRINT            # print counter
PUSH 5           # check if counter == 5
CMPJMP(loop)     # if not, continue loop
HALT 0
```

### 예: 함수 호출

```
PUSH 10          # arg1
PUSH 20          # arg2
CALL(add_fn)     # call add(10, 20)
PRINT            # print result [30]
HALT 0

(add_fn:)        # ADD는 이미 구현됨 (Week 4)
ADD              # arg1 + arg2
RET              # return
```

